#TEXT#
Set course for the nearest Starbase to replenish Photon Torpedoes. There are two 
starbases. Starbase 131 is in sector 01-03-01. Resume your original course or 
return to your original location. Try to time this so you are between assignments so 
as not to fail a mission.
#FINISH#
#LINKS#
