#HINT#
3

#TEXT#
Save the game at every opportunity. There are four main reasons: 
* You can lose the ship & crew in battle.
* I found the game crashed frequently and unpredictably.
* It is easy to get stuck after having performed the wrong action.
* You may complete the assignment, but when you check with Starfleet they are 
not completely happy with your performance. You will probably want to try again to 
do better.
